ives.-CREDIT_-Barry-Brecheisen_Getty-Images-and-Iwi-Onodera_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jamie-xx-and-Nia-Archives.-CREDIT_-Barry-Brecheisen_Getty-Images-and-Iwi-Onodera_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jamie-xx-and-Nia-Archives.-CREDIT_-Barry-Brecheisen_Getty-Images-and-Iwi-Onodera_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jamie-xx-and-Nia-Archives.-CREDIT_-Barry-Brecheisen_Getty-Images-and-Iwi-Onodera_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jamie-xx-and-Nia-Archives.-CREDIT_-Barry-Brecheisen_Getty-Images-and-Iwi-Onodera_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jamie-xx-and-Nia-Archives.-CREDIT_-Barry-Brecheisen_Getty-Images-and-Iwi-Onodera_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Jamie-xx-and-Nia-Archives.-CREDIT_-Barry-Brecheisen_Getty-Images-and-Iwi-Onodera_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a>重新混音了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-xx">Jamie xx</a>的“Waited All Night”。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jamie-xx-in-waves-review-3794408">Jamie xx – “In Waves”评论：舞池上众星云集的冥想</a></strong></li></ul><p>原曲取自他最近的专辑《In Waves》，由他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-xx">The xx</a>乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/romy-madley-croft">Romy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oliver-sim">Oliver Sim</a>主演。这是自乐队 2017 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/the-xx-i-see-you-1934222">I See You</a> 》以来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-jamie-xx-reunite-with-the-xx-bandmates-romy-and-oliver-sim-on-atmospheric-new-single-waiting-all-night-3794968">，三位艺术家首次一起出现在一首歌曲中</a>。</p><p>现在，Nia Archives 分享了她的充满丛林气息的版本“Waited All Night”，此前她和 Jamie 近几个月都向现场观众演奏过该版本。</p><p>关于混音，妮娅说：“将这首歌曲重新混音为我最喜欢的杰米的歌曲真是太兴奋了。”<br />新专辑。不得不在这个翻转上进入完全快乐的硬核模式，并且在过去几个月的所有美国/欧盟巡演日期中它一直在进行！”</p><p>看看下面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Jamie xx - Waited All Night ft. Romy &amp; Oliver Sim (Nia Archives Remix)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8ruwv4PVXf4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，Jamie xx 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jamie-xx-to-curate-own-day-at-londons-new-lido-festival-with-romy-arca-sampha-and-more-3807487">宣布他将作为首届头条新闻之一在 LIDO 音乐节上策划一天的活动</a>。他的阵容包括他的 xx 乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/romy">Romy</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/panda-bear">Panda Bear</a> 、John Glacier、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arca">Arca</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">Sampha</a> 、DJ Gigola、Shy One、Wookie 和 livwutang。</p><p>他目前还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jamie-xx-announces-2025-in-waves-world-tour-buy-tickets-3798679">进行“In Waves”世界巡演</a>。此次现场演出是为了支持他的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jamie-xx-in-waves-review-3794408">《In Waves》，</a>这是他自 2015 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/jamie-xx-on-debut-solo-album-in-colour-his-bright-bold-homage-to-london-nightlife-17406">《In Colour》以来的首张个人完整专辑。</a></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jamie-xx-in-waves-review-3794408">《In Waves》的四星评论</a>中， <em>《NME》</em>称这张唱片“比前作更加忧郁，而且也不那么令人兴奋。”但它可以说是一个更复杂的野兽，诞生于一个复杂的时代，但却是由一位专注于俱乐部简单、永恒乐趣的音乐家创作的。距离《In Colour》的成功已经近十年了，《In Waves》的推出让 Jamie xx 依然保持着蓬勃发展的状态。”</p><p>与此同时，Nia Archives 在今年早些时候发行了她获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-tv-and-radio-programme-announced-3785881">水星奖</a>提名的首张专辑《Silence Is Loud》，该专辑获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nia-archives-silence-is-loud-review-lyrics-tracklist-3616549"><em>NME</em>的四星好评</a>，Kyann-Sian Williams 写道：“她散发着自信，不再隐藏自己的声音她邪恶的制作技巧的背后。</p><p> “通过每个项目，妮娅都在为她在唱片中播下的想法和概念的种子浇水。而且，在她的首张专辑中，它们都绽放为一张丰富的、自我反思的唱片，展示了艺术家超越节拍的一面。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-nia-archives-exhilarating-remix-of-jamie-xxs-waited-all-night-3816148">查看 Nia Archives 对 Jamie xx 的《Waited All Night》的令人兴奋的混音版</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
